<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">国风·邶风·式微</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contson0e1fe871ec57">
式微，式微，胡不归？微君之故，胡为乎中露！<br />式微，式微，胡不归？微君之躬，胡为乎泥中！
</div>
</div>
