<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_ef488b31f706.aspx"><b>国风·秦风·驷驖</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonef488b31f706">
驷驖孔阜，六辔在手。公之媚子，从公于狩。<br />奉时辰牡，辰牡孔硕。公曰左之，舍拔则获。<br />游于北园，四马既闲。輶车鸾镳，载猃歇骄。
</div>
